FBIS3-380 "drafr044_d_94015" FBIS-AFR-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Mozambique New Political Party Founded, Supports Federalism MB0403185794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 1730 GMT 4 Mar 94 MB0403185794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] Another political party has been founded in Mozambique. It is called the Mozambique Internationalist Democratic Party, Pidemo, founded by Joao Kamacho. The party views federalism as the best system of government to guarantee the country's development.
